See Wiki for Documentation: https://github.com/brannala/ugnix/wiki

Static compiling library uGnix:
gcc -c uGnix.o
ar rcs libugnix.a uGnix.o

Using library uGnix:
gcc -c foo.c
gcc -o foo foo.o -L. -luGnix
